    <item>
      <title>特朗普将下令削减联邦政府职位，作为马斯克裁员计划的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-to-order-federal-job-cuts-as-part-of-musk-s-downsizing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普计划指示各机构配合伊隆·马斯克的政府削减成本计划，裁减员工，这是他削减联邦官僚机构的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-to-order-federal-job-cuts-as-part-of-musk-s-downsizing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:26:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬向伊隆·马斯克表示“感谢”，抨击特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/ken-griffin-says-thank-you-to-elon-musk-attacks-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Citadel 创始人肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 表示，他很感激伊隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 抽出时间来削减政府开支，但对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 总统的关税言论提出了直言不讳的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/ken-griffin-says-thank-you-to-elon-musk-attacks-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lutnick 正在探索“贸易工具”以应对欧洲 ESG 规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/lutnick-is-exploring-trade-tools-to-target-europe-s-esg-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提名的商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克 (Howard Lutnick) 表示，美国可能会使用“贸易工具”来报复影响美国公司的欧洲 ESG 法规。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/lutnick-is-exploring-trade-tools-to-target-europe-s-esg-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普准备和平计划 俄罗斯释放美国教师</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/russia-releases-american-teacher-as-trump-readies-peace-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫周二宣布，一名自 2021 年以来被俄罗斯拘留的美国人现已获释并返回美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/russia-releases-american-teacher-as-trump-readies-peace-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部长称津巴布韦尚未准备好采用单一货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/zimbabwe-isn-t-yet-ready-for-a-sole-currency-finance-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦财政部长姆图利·恩库贝 (Mthuli Ncube) 表示，这个南部非洲国家需要重新获得信贷额度，然后才能采用津巴布韦元作为其唯一货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/zimbabwe-isn-t-yet-ready-for-a-sole-currency-finance-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官称财政部数据限制适用于 DOGE，而不是 Bessent</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/judge-says-treasury-data-limit-applies-to-doge-not-bessent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼哈顿的一名法官同意，美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特应该被允许在诉讼期间访问敏感的联邦政府支付数据，尽管埃隆·马斯克的政府效率团队目前仍将被禁止访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/judge-says-treasury-data-limit-applies-to-doge-not-bessent</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:31:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普放松援助威胁；约旦将接收患病加沙儿童</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-eases-off-aid-threat-jordan-to-take-sick-gaza-children</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在约旦国王阿卜杜拉二世于白宫会议上同意接收 2,000 名来自加沙的患病儿童后，唐纳德·特朗普总统收回了停止向约旦提供美国援助的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-eases-off-aid-threat-jordan-to-take-sick-gaza-children</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 17:52:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福特首席执行官警告议员关税将带来“毁灭性”影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/ford-s-ceo-to-warn-lawmakers-of-devastating-tariff-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福特汽车公司首席执行官吉姆·法利将于周三前往华盛顿，警告国会议员，唐纳德·特朗普总统提出的对加拿大和墨西哥征收 25% 的关税将“摧毁”美国汽车业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/ford-s-ceo-to-warn-lawmakers-of-devastating-tariff-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 15:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“残酷事件”发生后，亚当斯市长寻求纽约人的信任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/nyc-mayor-ripped-by-rivals-as-doj-pushes-to-drop-bribery-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯表示，在特朗普政府指示检察官撤销对他的腐败指控后，他将面临政治对手的攻击，他将努力重新赢得纽约人的信任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/nyc-mayor-ripped-by-rivals-as-doj-pushes-to-drop-bribery-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 14:36:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯警告欧洲不要对新兴人工智能进行过度监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/vance-warns-europe-against-over-regulation-of-emerging-ai-field</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统 JD Vance 表示，特朗普政府将努力使美国成为人工智能的“全球黄金标准”，并对监管政治言论发出了强烈警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/vance-warns-europe-against-over-regulation-of-emerging-ai-field</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 10:36:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
